[SN]TITLE[SN]
Exposing cyber criminals' tricks

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
BBC Scotland Investigates: Gangsters.com will be broadcast on Wednesday 11 June, at 22:35 on BBC One Scotland, and for a week afterwards on the BBC iPlayer.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
10 June 2014 Last updated at 18:45 BST
Tony Sales, a former online fraudster who now advises businesses on how to protect themselves, shows the BBC's Samantha Poling one of the tricks used by cyber criminals to get hold of information.
